OL,3,CDWP's new bank account checking powers
OL,4,C'must have risk of over-reach
OL,5,Cmitigated'
OL,7,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,8,F(DWP) must make sure it uses its
OL,9,Fsignificant new bank account checking
OL,10,Fpowers proportionately because public
OL,11,Ftrust is at stake, according to a
OL,12,Fspending watchdog.
OL,14,FThe Public Accounts Committee (PAC)
OL,15,Fhighlighted how the DWP has been given
OL,16,Fpowers to compel banks and other
OL,17,Ffinancial institutions to provide
OL,18,Finformation to help verify a
OL,19,Fclaimant's eligibility and entitlement
OL,20,Fto benefits.
