OL,3,CDWP's new bank account checking powers
OL,4,C'must have risk of over-reach
OL,5,Cmitigated'
OL,7,FThe Public Authorities (Fraud, Error
OL,8,Fand Recovery) Act 2025 gives the
OL,9,FDepartment its new legal powers.
OL,11,FThe Department can force third parties
OL,12,Fto provide information when it is
OL,13,Fconducting criminal investigations,
OL,14,Fand in some cases recover money owed
OL,15,Fby people directly from their accounts
OL,16,Fwithout a court order.
OL,18,FBut the PAC said the DWP has not fully
OL,19,Fset out how it will use its powers in
OL,20,Fa way that supports public trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
