OL,7,FIn a report, it is calling for the
OL,8,Fdepartment to report in its annual
OL,9,Freport and accounts on how often it
OL,10,Fhas used the powers given to it in the
OL,11,F2025 Act, and with what impact.
OL,13,FThe PAC's report said: "The department
OL,14,Falso needs to improve its processes
OL,15,Fand controls to stop overpayments
OL,16,Farising in the first place and prevent
OL,17,Flosses to the taxpayer.
