OL,7,F"A key element of this is drawing on
OL,8,Fdata held by other government
OL,9,Fdepartments to help check claimants'
OL,10,Fentitlement to benefits."
OL,12,FThe report also highlighted how the
OL,13,FDWP has now committed that it will put
OL,14,Fright the cases of 26,000 carers
OL,15,Fincorrectly recorded as having
OL,16,Foverpaid carer's allowance.
OL,18,FThe PAC's inquiry heard that it will
OL,19,Ftake around two years to identify all
OL,20,Fthose affected, with 200,000 cases to
OL,21,Fbe reviewed.
