OL,7,FIts report said: "Unfulfilled
OL,8,Feligibility was estimated to be #3.7
OL,9,Fbillion in 2024`25, up from #3.1
OL,10,Fbillion in 2023`24. It particularly
OL,11,Faffects claimants of disability
OL,12,Fbenefits, such as personal
OL,13,Findependence payment, who fail to
OL,14,Freport that their condition has
OL,15,Fworsened."
OL,17,FThe PAC said said the DWP should
OL,18,Fevaluate how well it is encouraging
OL,19,Fclaimants to report changes in their
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
