OL,7,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chair of
OL,8,Fthe Public Accounts Committee, said:
OL,9,F"Make no mistake, the DWP's new powers
OL,10,Fto reach further into citizens' lives
OL,11,Fare significant.
