OL,5,Cmitigated'
OL,7,F"Our committee of course firmly
OL,8,Fsupports Government in its
OL,9,Fresponsibility to ensure people are
OL,10,Fpaid the correct benefits. But it is
OL,11,Fessential that these extensive new
OL,12,Fpowers ` of compulsion of disclosure
OL,13,Fover banks and financial institutions,
OL,14,Fof recovering funds directly from
OL,15,Fpeople's accounts without the aid of
OL,16,Fthe courts ` have the risk of over-
OL,17,Freach mitigated against right from the
OL,18,Foutset.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
