OL,3,CDWP's new bank account checking powers
OL,4,C'must have risk of over-reach
OL,5,Cmitigated'
OL,7,F"Indeed, a separate element of our
OL,8,Freport, which saw a welcome apology
OL,9,Ffrom the DWP's permanent secretary to
OL,10,Fall those carers wronged by his
OL,11,Fdepartment, demonstrates the impact
OL,12,Fthat wrongly-implemented powers can
OL,13,Fhave on people's lives.
OL,15,F"Our report finds beyond doubt that
OL,16,Fcurrent ambitions to address
OL,17,Funacceptable levels of benefit fraud
OL,18,Fand error are not stretching enough.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
