OL,3,CDWP's new bank account checking powers
OL,4,C'must have risk of over-reach
OL,5,Cmitigated'
OL,7,F"More could be done on a cross-
OL,8,Fgovernment basis to improve the
OL,9,Faccuracy of benefit payments, and the
OL,10,FDepartment has not yet taken a proper
OL,11,Flook in the mirror to address official
OL,12,Ferror rather than focusing entirely on
OL,13,Fclaimants.
OL,15,F"But our report marks the now 37th
OL,16,Fyear in which the DWP has had its
OL,17,Faccounts qualified by the UK's chief
OL,18,Fauditor due to material levels of
OL,19,Ffraud and error.
