OL,7,F"As PAC chair, I would say to the
OL,8,Fdepartment's leadership directly: we
OL,9,Fare just three years away from what
OL,10,Fwould be a sad and embarrassing
OL,11,Fmilestone. Urgent action must be taken
OL,12,Fper our recommendations for the DWP to
OL,13,Fhave something to celebrate in the
OL,14,Fyears to come."
OL,16,FA DWP spokesperson said: "We have
OL,17,Fintroduced major reforms to ensure
OL,18,Fpeople are paid the correct benefits,
OL,19,Fto recover overpayments and to help
OL,20,Fsave billions of pounds for the
OL,21,Ftaxpayer.
