OL,7,F"The powers in the Fraud, Error and
OL,8,FRecovery Act have numerous safeguards
OL,9,Fand will be independently overseen.
OL,11,F"We will not have access to claimants'
OL,12,Fbank accounts when checking they are
OL,13,Freceiving the correct benefits.
OL,15,F"We are forecasting an ambitious
OL,16,Freduction in fraud and error levels to
OL,17,F2.8% by 2028-29, the lowest level
OL,18,Fsince tax credits were introduced in
OL,19,F2003-04."
